screen_desc: A mobile shopping app screen displays various product recommendations. At the top, there is a search bar with the text "Search or ask a question." Below, a banner reads "Refresh your home - Deals under $50" with an image of a bedroom. The next section shows product recommendations: "Keep shopping for Laptop stands," "Recommended deal for you" featuring a laptop stand, and "Glow up under $25" featuring a facial roller. Further down, there are more product suggestions under "Keep shopping for" with images of laptop stands and lap desks. At the bottom, there is a navigation bar with icons for home, user account, cart, menu, and notifications.
